Dear Team,
Greetings of the day,

I am writing this latter to notifying that I am resigning from my position
as "General Manager" at Impression Furniture Govindpura Showroom .

The last date of my employment is 10th March 2025 .

I appreciate the opportunities I have been given at this organisation and
your professional guidance and support .

I wish impression furniture and entire associate team success in the future
.

I am taking this steps due to some of mine personal reasons where I am
unable to continue with you from immediate response hope you will
understand.

Please update I have been completed all the assignments already which were
in my hand and important thinks has been updated to my current team .

Also note that I have not taken any advance or any imprest money from the
company and even not have any belonging gadget of company with me like
desktop or laptop or any important documents with me which needed to
handover .

From today onwards I will not available physicaly with you but always
available on call or massage (virtually) for company if needed any
information or suggestions for any matter for well wishesh of the company .

Again I wish Best of luck for the bright future of company and the entire
associate team .

Always yours,
Narendra Agrawal
Ex General Manager Showroom
Impression Furniture Govindpura
